snippet.title: Purps plays: Func Xmas Jam 2017, Part 1.
snippet.description:
No commentary.
Map is "A Warm Welcome Home" by Bal.
Don't watch this if you don't want to spoil parts of the Func Xmasjam 2017 map pack.


You can download at the map pack at https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/func_xmasjam2017.html
I'll tune up my recording settings for future uploads. At the moment, I'm just recording with my streaming settings, which aren't great.

I go live on Twitch sometimes at: https://www.twitch.tv/badluckbeast
